，但AI幻觉增加了医患间的冲突和不信任；大模型给医生减负也减轻了医院管理成本，但大模型的实施和维护成本高昂；生态开放降低了医疗大模型的入局门槛，但大模型的迭代需要大量高质量数据，强者恒强的故事仍在上演。 小模型打败大模型？患者挑战专家？医疗AI需要冷思考"},"attached_info":"CkII4s+I9ovxx6YqEAMaCTExMzc1NjQ4NyCkupS+BjAAOIIBQA5yCzEzOTA1NzAyMDEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"122 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8dd814eacc99118b936cd731ef7abfde_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1741238416.927770","card_id":"Q_458627547","target":{"id":458627547,"title":"菜鸟驿站为什么那么多转让的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/458627547","type":"question","created":1620605391,"answer_count":586,"follower_count":2752,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[38918,62443,181050],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I4s+I9ovxx6YqEAMaCDY0MTk3NjYxIM/z4YQGMAA4wBVAD3IJNDU4NjI3NTQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"118 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8f1ffefd7ca940fb53b7078e8b08a184_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1741238416.928531","card_id":"Q_14149145601","target":{"id":14149145601,"title":"如何看待政府工作报告吹风会上提到，「很多人工智能的应用在加速落地，大家都感到很振奋」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14149145601","type":"question","created":1741170502,"answer_count":63,"follower_count":130,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[188574,696408,1386211,3540600,3844268],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"3月5日，国务院新闻办就解读《政府工作报告》举行吹风会。 会上，《政府工作报告》起草组成员、国务院研究室副主任陈昌盛说，去年《政府工作报告》首次提出要实施“人工智能+”行动。春节前后，在很多科创企业、科研机构和各级政府共同努力下，中国的人工智能产业确实跑出了“加速度”。比如，DeepSeek全球出圈、宇树科技的机器人在春晚上扭秧歌，大家都在问为什么“杭州六小龙”会一下子火起来。很多人工智能的应用在加速落